Videorec is a mission controlled video recorder written for Flash 10, Red5 and Google App Engine (GAE).

Flash client
	* Configurable through configuration xml file
	* Sends request to GAE-application for approved and valid rtmp host and stream
	* Opens a rtmp connection and stream to record and preview recorder material

GAE-application
	* Validates flash client requests
	* Sends rtmp host, stream id and where to find recorded material to flash client
	* Validates stream id from Red5-application

Red5-application
	* Validates stream id from Red5-application
	* Receives stream data for recording
	* Sends stream data for preview
	* Stores recorded data on server in a public directory